Method-1:-
    Use redis:-

    Pros:-
    Simple

    Cons:-
    Latency

Method-2:-
    Use In-memory:-

    Pros:-
    Cost can be slightly less as compared to method 1

    Cons:-
    Locking mechanism can be complex to implement with can lead to extra cost as the training will happen on stale data.

Method-3:-

    Use Dynamo DB:-

    Pros:-
    Simple to implement

    Cons:-
    Cost will be very high in the learning phase.



My Recommendation:-
Method-2 

Because its the balanace of simplicity, cost, throughput, scale and latency.

